column4: Intel shares could rise 25 percent in next year: Barron's
column5: NEW YORK Intel Corp's 	 shift to higher-growth businesses such as server chips and embedded chips for cars could drive a 25 increase in its shares in a year  according to a report on Sunday in the financial publication Barron's.
